{"tid":2122944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"康文署促勿到泳灘 已加強圍封","createTime":"2020-07-24T09:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T10:33:39.000Z","uid":166360,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2924d3347ea04cf5c2f16443dc87530e4b6379","tid":2122944,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"康文署促勿到泳灘 已加強圍封<br />\n2020-07-24 HKT 16:24<br />\n<br />\n＂康文署再次強烈呼籲，市民響應政府呼籲盡量留在家中，切勿前往已關閉的泳灘游泳或日光浴，以減少人流聚集，減低病毒在社區傳播的風險，亦避免發生意外。＂<br />\n<br />\n＂署方強調，進入已封閉的沙灘是違法行為，可被檢控，將加派人員在相關地點巡邏，如有關人士不聽從勸喻，會視乎情況採取檢控行動，如果行為涉及刑事毀壞，會尋求警方協助。 ＂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539670-20200724.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539670-20200724.htm&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=1e2c5731\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539670-20200724.htm&h=abfdf5d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539670-20200724.htm</a>"},{"pid":"73a08c5ac467a339c02ffd4ad9d26c346bec0f1e","tid":2122944,"uid":100772,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"沙灘違法<br />\n咁去碼頭游得唔得"},{"pid":"4d8a75ee40f7d4211b46fb1a6c0d0aebe59a7c7a","tid":2122944,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解剩係識得封入面 唔封出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 好無助"},{"pid":"b74b39a0a4d0de677c1c1f8410b005594fa7b168","tid":2122944,"uid":274435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":